data.description: Welcome to this charming and chic condo, located in the heart of the Central District with breathtaking city views. This historical Victorian home was originally built in 1900 and was remodeled into 3 condos. Tall ceilings and large windows pour in natural light into this 2bed/1bath gem. One dedicated parking space and direct entry into unit makes it feel more like a home than a condo. Well-cared for with open living, spacious bedrooms, large closets, plenty of storage. Updates include new flooring, remodeled bathroom, modern dining light, new water heater. Easy downtown commute and convenient location near restaurants, coffee, shops, PCC, and Lake Washington. Units in this gorgeous complex rarely come on the market. Assumable loan option.
